<p>Now in the above cases we will see the flow of influence from <img class=
=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/211284f68205c3e66773eaf026f=
32a0acdd3dfb3.png" alt=3D"A"> to <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.o=
rg/_images/math/4db5b6e16e06f929ce3f675c5e535d06ffb02ff7.png" alt=3D"C"> un=
der various cases.</p>
<ol class=3D"arabic simple">
<li><p><strong>Causal:</strong> In the general case when we make any change=
s in the variable <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math=
/211284f68205c3e66773eaf026f32a0acdd3dfb3.png" alt=3D"A">, it will have eff=
ect of variable <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4=
bc3e94a67870b41b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> (as we discussed ab=
ove) and this change in <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_image=
s/math/4bc3e94a67870b41b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> will change=
 the values in <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4d=
b5b6e16e06f929ce3f675c5e535d06ffb02ff7.png" alt=3D"C">. One other possible =
case can be when <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/=
4bc3e94a67870b41b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> is observed i.e. w=
e know the value of <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/ma=
th/4bc3e94a67870b41b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B">. So, in this ca=
se any change in <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/=
211284f68205c3e66773eaf026f32a0acdd3dfb3.png" alt=3D"A"> won=E2=80=99t affe=
ct <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4bc3e94a67870b=
41b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> since we already know the value.=
 And hence there won=E2=80=99t be any change in <img class=3D"math" src=3D"=
https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4db5b6e16e06f929ce3f675c5e535d06ffb02ff7.png=
" alt=3D"C"> as it depends only on <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy=
.org/_images/math/4bc3e94a67870b41b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B">.
Mathematically we can say that: <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.or=
g/_images/math/804ca24d5efc37bccd5c9d4b2d2d16a6a0244e58.png" alt=3D"(A \per=
p C | B)">.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Evidential:</strong> Similarly in this case also observing <=
img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4bc3e94a67870b41b7=
c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> renders <img class=3D"math" src=3D"h=
ttps://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4db5b6e16e06f929ce3f675c5e535d06ffb02ff7.png"=
 alt=3D"C"> independent of <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_im=
ages/math/211284f68205c3e66773eaf026f32a0acdd3dfb3.png" alt=3D"A">. Otherwi=
se when <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4bc3e94a6=
7870b41b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> is not observed the influen=
ce flows from <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/211=
284f68205c3e66773eaf026f32a0acdd3dfb3.png" alt=3D"A"> to <img class=3D"math=
" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4db5b6e16e06f929ce3f675c5e535d06ffb=
02ff7.png" alt=3D"C">. Hence <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_=
images/math/804ca24d5efc37bccd5c9d4b2d2d16a6a0244e58.png" alt=3D"(A \perp C=
 | B)">.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Common Evidence:</strong> This case is a bit different from =
the others. When <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/=
4bc3e94a67870b41b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> is not observed an=
y change in <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/21128=
4f68205c3e66773eaf026f32a0acdd3dfb3.png" alt=3D"A"> reflects some change in=
 <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4bc3e94a67870b41=
b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> but not in <img class=3D"math" src=
=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4db5b6e16e06f929ce3f675c5e535d06ffb02ff7=
.png" alt=3D"C">. Let=E2=80=99s take the example of <img class=3D"math" src=
=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/e3f78f1524a6156f60f906623ab76e0b05aa31ec=
.png" alt=3D"D \rightarrow G \leftarrow I">. In this case if we increase th=
e difficulty of the course the probability of getting a higher grade reduce=
s but this has no effect on the intelligence of the student. But when <img =
class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4bc3e94a67870b41b7c201=
79693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> is observed let=E2=80=99s say that the s=
tudent got a good grade. Now if we
increase the difficulty of the course this will increase the probability of=
 the student to be intelligent since we already know that he got a good gra=
de. Hence in this case <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images=
/math/3aafac76efa120f4c16138c8acc877c8c4c5ca17.png" alt=3D"(A \perp C)"> an=
d <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/592cae77aa1e512=
603120dfe2670c0679cd38380.png" alt=3D"( A \not\perp C | B)">. This structur=
e is also commonly known as V structure.</p></li>
<li><p><strong>Common Cause:</strong> The influence flows from <img class=
=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/211284f68205c3e66773eaf026f=
32a0acdd3dfb3.png" alt=3D"A"> to <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.o=
rg/_images/math/4db5b6e16e06f929ce3f675c5e535d06ffb02ff7.png" alt=3D"C"> wh=
en <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4bc3e94a67870b=
41b7c20179693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> is not observed. But when <img c=
lass=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4bc3e94a67870b41b7c2017=
9693e889251e2c136.png" alt=3D"B"> is observed and change in <img class=3D"m=
ath" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/211284f68205c3e66773eaf026f32a0a=
cdd3dfb3.png" alt=3D"A"> doesn=E2=80=99t affect <img class=3D"math" src=3D"=
https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4db5b6e16e06f929ce3f675c5e535d06ffb02ff7.png=
" alt=3D"C"> since it=E2=80=99s only dependent on <img class=3D"math" src=
=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/4bc3e94a67870b41b7c20179693e889251e2c136=
.png" alt=3D"B">. Hence here also <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.=
org/_images/math/30824d99dc274a991e391e3f0abef1be0e008d5b.png" alt=3D"( A \=
perp C | B)">.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Let=E2=80=99s not see a few examples for finding the independencies in a=
 newtork using pgmpy:</p>
<div class=3D"nbinput docutils container">
<div class=3D"prompt highlight-none notranslate"><div class=3D"highlight"><=
