<p>There can be cases in which we want to compute the conditional distribut=
ion let=E2=80=99s say <img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/=
math/b7980ba95b13192ee645bc39aa10c614ee4bace5.png" alt=3D"P(G | D=3D0, I=3D=
1)">. In such cases we need to modify our equations a bit:</p>
<p><img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/3f4c9519a58dc1=
0e05c1c18ab274505cbe592750.png" alt=3D"P(G | D=3D0, I=3D1) =3D \sum_L \sum_=
S P(L|G) * P(S| I=3D1) * P(G| D=3D0, I=3D1) * P(D=3D0) * P(I=3D1)"></p>
<p><img class=3D"math" src=3D"https://pgmpy.org/_images/math/ea9afa2989d40b=
f6984dfbb44e70c2f2bd74a9a5.png" alt=3D"P(G | D=3D0, I=3D1) =3D P(D=3D0) * P=
(I=3D1) * P(G | D=3D0, I=3D1) * \sum_L P(L | G) * \sum_S P(S | I=3D1)"></p>
