ttps://pgmpy.org/detailed_notebooks/2.%20Bayesian%20Networks.html#Predictin=
g-values-from-new-data-points" title=3D"Link to this heading">=C2=B6</a></h=
4>
<p>Predicting values from new data points is quite similar to computing the=
 conditional probabilities. We need to query for the variable that we need =
to predict given all the other features. The only difference is that rather=
